      <br />
      <p class="mb-8">Get to know your cycle, using your own words, without worrying that the data will end up in the hands of Facebook and the likes.</p>
      <a href="https://my.usepow.app/signup/" class="no-underline mb-64 font-semibold text-white bg-red-700 hover:bg-red-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-red-300 rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5 dark:bg-red-600 dark:hover:bg-red-700 focus:outline-none dark:focus:ring-red-800">GET STARTED</a>
